         <en><![CDATA[To provide more hooks to GLPI plugins using runkit integration. In particular currently providing pre_show_item and post_show_item for Ticket, Computer and Reminder items

Added pre_show_item and post_show_item to TicketFollowup and CommonGLPI. Added show_form_buttons and show_form_header to TicketFollowup.

This plugin is currentlyused by plugin 'lock'. https://github.com/tomolimo/lock

Currently tested with: 
GLPI 0.83, 0.85 and 0.90
PHP 5.3, 5.4.

Note: needs PHP module 'runkit' ]]></en>
